<BaseLayout title="Who We Are" description="wART Radio is volunteer-run community radio serving Marshall and Madison County, NC. Learn about us and how to volunteer.">
	<section class="container">
		<h1>Who We Are</h1>

		<div class="card">
			<h2>Our Mission</h2>
			<p>wART Radio is community radio by and for the people of Marshall and Madison County, North Carolina. We're volunteer-run, listener-supported, and committed to local voices and music you won't hear anywhere else.</p>
		</div>

		<div class="card">
			<h2>Volunteer With Us</h2>
			<p>Have a question? Want to host a show or help behind the scenes? We're always looking for volunteers.</p>
			<p><a href="/contact/">Contact us</a> to get involved.</p>
		</div>

		<div class="card">
			<h2>Our Location</h2>
			<p>After a short period broadcasting from  CHC/Reclaim Madison, we are now and continuing to bring you local community radio from the campus of AB Tech Madison. Our former studio in the little red caboose was damaged severely in the floods from Helene, but we're still on the air.</p>
		</div>

		<div class="listen-live">
			<h2>Listen Live</h2>
			<a href="http://station.voscast.com/5530050e0a38b/" class="listen-btn" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Listen now</a>
		</div>
	</section>
</BaseLayout>
